Alternative single-reference coupled cluster approaches for multireference problems: The simpler, the better
J. Chem. Phys. 134 , 224102 (2011); https://doi.org/10.1063/1.3598471
Francesco A. Evangelista a)
more... View Affiliations

    Institut für Physikalische Chemie, Universität Mainz , D-55099 Mainz, Germany

    a) Electronic mail: evangeli@uni-mainz.de .

